HEADWORD: Unseven
<hw>Un*sev"en</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>seven</ets>.]</ety> <def>To render other than
seven; to make to be no longer seven.</def> <mark>[Obs. & R.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧To <xex>unseven</xex> the sacraments of the church of
Rome.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Fuller.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

